# DEPLOYMENT STEPS (Manual via Railway Dashboard)
# ==============================================================================

STEPS:

1. Go to: https://railway.app/dashboard

2. Select Project: "election-fraud-detection"

3. Click "+ Add Service"
   - Select "GitHub Repo"
   - Search: "Online-Voting-System"
   - Select: "yogeshmagatam/Online-Voting-System"
   - Branch: "feature/yogesh/login"
   - Wait 5-7 minutes for build

4. Add MongoDB Service
   - "+ Add Service" → "Add from Marketplace" → "MongoDB"
   - Wait 2-3 minutes for provisioning

5. Configure Environment Variables
   - Click Python service → "Variables" tab
   - Add all variables above
   - Click "Deploy" to apply

6. Get Backend URL
   - Click Python service → "Settings" → "Domains"
   - Copy the URL (looks like: https://your-app-xxxx.railway.app)

7. Update Vercel Frontend
   - Go to: https://vercel.com/yogeshmagatams-projects/online-voting-system
   - Settings → Environment Variables
   - Update REACT_APP_API_URL with Railway backend URL
   - Save and Redeploy

8. Test
   - Go to: https://online-voting-system-six-flax.vercel.app
   - Register → Login → Vote → Success! ✅

